@startuml

title AircraftWar DAO Pattern (Leaderboard)

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

package "application" {
  class Game {
    - score : int
    - scoreRecordDao : ScoreRecordDao
    + checkResultAction() : void
    + saveAndPrintLeaderboard() : void
  }
}

package "dao" {
  class ScoreRecord {
    - playerName : String
    - score : int
    - recordTime : LocalDateTime
    + toStorageLine() : String
    + fromStorageLine(line : String) : ScoreRecord
  }

  interface ScoreRecordDao {
    + getAllRecords() : List<ScoreRecord>
    + addRecord(record : ScoreRecord) : void
  }

  class FileScoreRecordDao {
    - storageFile : Path
    + getAllRecords() : List<ScoreRecord>
    + addRecord(record : ScoreRecord) : void
    - resolveStorageFile() : Path
  }
}

ScoreRecordDao <|.. FileScoreRecordDao
Game ..> ScoreRecordDao : use
FileScoreRecordDao ..> ScoreRecord : read/write

note right of ScoreRecordDao
  DAO Pattern
  - separate business logic from data access
  - allow swapping data source implementation
end note

@enduml
